    "Analogous to the structure of the brain, raw information is progressively processed and featureextracted through interconnected hidden neuron layers.",
    "Deep neural networks utilize numerous neurons to process input data, attaining higher-level representations and abstractions.",
    "Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) (Kowsari et al., 2019) are widely used deep learning models in NLP.",
    "Comprising convolutional layers, pooling layers, and fully connected layers, CNNs efficiently extract local features from images.",
    "Pooling layers reduce feature dimensions while maintaining positional invariance, and fully connected layers map the extracted features to the final output."
